# throughputKey

**Type Property**

A key with a corresponding value that indicates the speed of data processing, in bytes per second.

## Declaration

```swift
static let throughputKey: ProgressUserInfoKey
```

## Discussion

If present, the autogenerated [doc://com.apple.foundation/documentation/Foundation/Progress/localizedAdditionalDescription] uses the value to provide a string that presents more information.

## Using General Keys

- **estimatedTimeRemainingKey**: A key with a corresponding value that represents the time remaining, in seconds.
